<HEAD>
<TITLE>The average cost of a gun is about $200</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<P>
<CENTER><a href="/atr/tax-presentation/hotloped.html">next</a> | 1 of 8 | <a href="/atr/">home</a><br><FONT SIZE=6><a href="/atr/tax-presentation/paymeal.html">The average cost of a restaurant meal
is about $40</a><BR>
</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>$11 goes directly to taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>$29 covers all other costs of preparing and
serving the meal<BR>
<BR>
<img src="/atr/sept96/food.gif">
</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><U><FONT SIZE=4>Taxes imposed on meals: <BR>
</FONT></U></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Federal Income Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Federal Payroll Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>State Income Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>State Sales and Use Taxes </FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Unemployment Insurance Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Workmen's Compensation Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>State Property Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Business License Taxes and Fees</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Local Property Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Local Income Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Telephone Excise Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Utility Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Liquor Excise Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Food and Beverage Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
