<FONT SIZE=3><CENTER><B>C-News Subscriptions</B></CENTER><P>
    C-News is the 'net's biggest and best conservative mailing list. Each weekday, C-News subscribers receive 8 to 10 e-mail messages with news and information about conservative politics. To subscribe, just follow the directions below.  Or, <A HREF="/cnews/info.html">read</A> some more about C-News.<P>
    To subscribe to C-News, send the following message to <a href="mailto:majordomo@world.std.com">majordomo@world.std.com</a>:<p>
<CENTER>SUBSCRIBE C-NEWS</CENTER><p>

    To subscribe to the C-News digest (a method by which you recieve one 
compilation message per day, rather than 10-12 individual messages), send 
the following message to <a href="mailto:majordomo@world.std.com">majordomo@world.std.com</a>:<p>
<CENTER>SUBSCRIBE C-NEWS-DIGEST</CENTER><p>
    To unsubscribe from C-News or C-News-Digest, send a message to 
<a href="mailto:majordomo@world.std.com">majordomo@world.std.com</a> 
saying:<p>
<CENTER>UNSUBSCRIBE C-NEWS<p>
or<p>
UNSUBSCRIBE C-NEWS-DIGEST</CENTER><p></FONT>

