Subject: NEW: STERN-GLANCE - Public Relations Newsletter<P>

STERN-GLANCE on listproc@COMQUEST.COM<P>

   Stern and Company is now making its newsletter, "a stern glance"
   available via a distribution mailing list. This periodical
   provides economic, political, and public relations perspectives.
   Newsletters are issued monthly and distributed to members
   of the mailing list; this is NOT a discussion list.<P>

   Newsletters are also posted on our Web Site at:<P>

         <A HREF="http://www.sternandcompany.com/stern/newsletter/">http://www.sternandcompany.com/stern/newsletter/</A><P>

   Stern and Company develops and implements strategic and highly
   defined corporate communications programs for its clients.  Its
   practice comprises corporate strategies, investor relations,
   crisis communications, media relations, public affairs, litigation
   support, government relations and merger and acquisition
   communications.  These and other topics are frequently covered in
   the newsletter.<P>

   To subscribe, send a message to listproc@comquest.com with the
   following as the first line in the body of the message:<P>

         SUBSCRIBE STERN-GLANCE your name<P>

   For example:  subscribe stern-glance Pat Smith<P>

   Owner:  Jeff Stacey  stacey@comquest.com<P>


