<p><br>
<center><h2>Footing the Bill</h2></center>
<p><br>
<center>
<img src="/abic/images/ftb-7-22-96.gif" BORDER=0></a>
<p>
Source: <a href="http://www.rollcall.com">Roll Call</a>, July 18, 1996, p. 1.
<p>
*This figure does not include structural renovations to the room in the Hart Senate Office building.  Those figures were unavailable.
<p>
